text: Nabii Mucammadow ku Rabbi magaalol maray kaal koroosite yibbixeeh, digaaleeh kah bayse innah, keenik kalah aka magaaloolih maray isi nafsi koroosannut yudlume, digaaleeh ken bayseh Yallal koroositeeniih Yallih farmoytit dirabboyseenimih sabbatah, Diggah Nabiyow ku Rabbih xibix digaal√°l qansaru leeh gibdih
